text: Tömür Dawamat (; ; June 16, 1927 – December 19, 2018) was a Chinese politician. He was born in Toksun, Xinjiang, China. Dawamat was the chairman of the Xinjiang Uyghur Autonomous Region of the People's Republic of China from 1985 to 1993. Dawamat died on December 19, 2018 at the age of 91. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:2018 deaths Category:20th-century Chinese politicians
